@ENDNODE

@NODE Tips "Some Infos"


Sometimes when Library Window and JumpDump Window are open and you double click
on new library to show, Asp Crash 8-(
I have tasted a lot my source code whitout find any bug, sorry.
If this happened reboot your system and before a double click on new library
close JumpDump Window.

@ENDNODE


